   <talk_paragraph index="n035_soceress_master_tiana-accepting" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_SoceressTiana.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n035_soceress_master_tiana-accepting-a" mid="6" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="5"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Sorceress Tiana$<BR>We might be able to revive the barren Forest of Death using that purification device.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n035_soceress_master_tiana-accepting-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_SoceressTiana.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n035_soceress_master_tiana-accepting-acceptted" mid="8" select_type="3" />
      <talk_question mid="7"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Sorceress Tiana$<BR>The Ancients knew how to cleanse poison, and they built a purification device based on their knowledge.<BR> That document has details about that purification facility.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n035_soceress_master_tiana-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_SoceressTiana.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n035_soceress_master_tiana-1-a" mid="51" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="9"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Sorceress Tiana$<BR>According to the research notes, the purification device is at Prayer's Resting Place. We need two items to activate it -- the White Purity Orb found in the innermost area of the Sanctuary Core and the Purification Device Key.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n035_soceress_master_tiana-1-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_SoceressTiana.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n035_soceress_master_tiana-1-b" mid="52" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="10"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Sorceress Tiana$<BR>After getting the White Purity Orb, you need to get the Purification Device Key. Manticore Keruru, the guardian of the purification device, has that key.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n035_soceress_master_tiana-1-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_SoceressTiana.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n035_soceress_master_tiana-1-" mid="79" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Sorceress Tiana$<BR>Go and get the orb from the Sanctuary Core. I will be reviewing the research notes in the meantime.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
